  "detailed_description": "Online multiplayer chicken racing game. Challenge your friends to see who can make the most money! Need to settle an argument? He who’s chicken wins, word is final.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures include:<br />\r\n- Place bets on chickens.<br />\r\n- Train your chickens to improve their chances.<br />\r\n- Sneakily sabotage the race.<br />\r\n- Try to win the most cash.<br />\r\n- Watch your chickens race, complete with photo finish.<br />\r\n- Features famous chickens such as Cluck Norris, Nugget, and many more.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHappy racing!",
